{"tid":1697503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港靠你班暴徒食撚得屎啦","createTime":"2019-11-07T01:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:31:13.000Z","uid":313635,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"26c57dad1f274cbf3c0ea6a6f238317de6a8ce39","tid":1697503,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:53:27.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你地老母呀，乜撚嘢十一.十 搞7區開花<br />\n你老味我第二日唔洗返工呀，你班甲曱日撚日喺度搞事破壞法治 屌你老母臭西<br />\n我警告你地呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪撚<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搞地鐵下面d月台幕門呀，消防設備間房呀，d電鑬呀，信號燈，路軌呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地鐵日日成百萬人次，你班暴徒成日搞<br />\n痴撚線㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我星期一要返工架，你咁搞係咪要全香港人唔返工同你地班甲曱攬炒呀<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街咁搞，政府遲早搞個獨立調查委員會清算你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e9d274e327f7e5b0d23eed2220e674f8ef80e5","tid":1697503,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce70d66f7319bce524e235268fb6c7126ea88cc1","tid":1697503,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d7f3449a87a71092f6b0d67f6990f83e868568","tid":1697503,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T02:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a2662387e759d22f1823f7bdb3d654bd510017","tid":1697503,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike